snippet.title: Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Anu-Nikhil की हुयी सगाई | Sneak Peek | Colors TV
snippet.description:
Anu-Nikhil की हुयी सगाई

Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Anu-Nikhil की हुयी सगाई | Sneak Peek | Colors TV

-------------------

Abandoned as a newborn by her own heartless mother and raised by her resilient maasi, Shruti, Mannat grows up to be a passionate and ambitious chef, unaware of her mysterious origins. Her journey intertwines with that of Vikrant, a successful buisnessman (restaurateur), as they bond over their love for cooking amidst the vibrant backdrop of Mumbai's chawls and elite culinary spaces. Mannat’s biological mother is none other than Aishwarya, a wealthy and manipulative woman determined to keep her secrets buried who is also Mannat's boss at Mezbaani where she works as a junior chef. Life takes a dramatic turn when Mannat discovers Shruti is not her biological mother, propelling her on a desperate quest to save Shruti’s life by finding her real mother for a liver transplant. Amidst these revelations, Mannat finds her strongest support in Vikrant, the prince charming of her life, who stands by her side, offering unwavering encouragement as she navigates the challenges life throws her way. As Mannat’s rising career, Shruti’s failing health, and the revelations of a hidden past collide, Mannat faces a whirlwind of love, betrayal, and self-discovery. Will her dreams and resilience help her overcome the storm, or will the weight of her past keep her from achieving her destiny?


Main Cast and Their Characters:
Ayesha Singh as Mannat
Adnan Khan(Vikrant
Mona Vasu as Aishwarya
Sharain Khanduja as Mallika
Mamta Verma as Shruti
Delnaaz Irani as Harneet
Hasan Zaidi as Gagan
Karan Godhwami as Puneet
Swati Anand as Neetu
Rushad Rana as Rony

From Honeymoon to Politics – A Unique Interview with Married Couple Dilip Ghosh and Rinku Majumder
Watch Now: Exclusive Interview with Dilip Ghosh and Wife Rinku Majumder | First Time After Marriage

For the first time after their wedding, BJP leader Dilip Ghosh appears exclusively on Sangbad Pratidin Digital with his wife Rinku Majumder. From candid moments of their honeymoon to deep dives into political opinions, witness the never-seen-before side of this power couple. Don’t miss this heartwarming and honest conversation blending love, life, and leadership.

Song Lyrics In Hindi

मीठी मीठी बोलै बांगरो आंखां मै तेरे जहर भरा
ती खीती खी तकै ना गणी मरजा णी तनै मा र गरा
देशी जूती पैंट ला जो सूट गजब का या र करा
द्होद्होरै आया हा मी भर दे फेर यो हो या हरा -भरा
फेर बा तां तै  ल छो लै बां गरो
मीठी -मीठी बो लै बां गरो  मीठी मीठी बोलै बांगरो
तू  लया ,सुख अपणा हो या
सा ची रै मेरा सपना हो या
कॉ लम I बणया तू मेरी थो ङी -थो ङी मेरे  ल की मखणा हो या
फेर ला    चखणा हो या तू भर-भर जो  तो लै बां गरो 
ठी -मी ठी बो लै बां गरो  मीठी मीठी बो लै बां गरो 
या ली बणकै घर मै आईए
पेजी गेयां ला ड लडा ईए
मेरी हो का गेयां सजै रै बैठैक ,भाज - भाज तू आग बणाईए
फेर मां मेरी न ममी - ममी बो लै बां गरो
मीठी मीठी बोलै बां गरो  मीठी मीठी बो लै बां गरो

Song Lyrics In English 

mithi mithi bole bangro aankhaan mai tere jaher bharaya
teekhi - teekhi takai nagani marajani tanai maar garya
 desi jooti paint  palazo  suit  gajab ka tyaar kara
 Dhorai aajya hami bharde pher sab kuchh hojya hara -bhara 
 pher bataan tai  ya dil chholai baangaro

 mithi mithi bole bangro aankhaan mai tere jaher bharaya

 tu miljya ,sukh apna ho jya 
 sachee rai mera sapna hojya 
  banaya tu meri thodi thodi  mere dil ki makhna hojya 
 Chakhna hojya mitha laadu tole bangro

 banke byali ghar mai aayiye
 pejee gelta laad ladaiye
 hoke gelya sajai rai baithaik ,bhaj bhajke tu aag banaiye

The wait is finally over—Saunkan Saunkanay 2 is coming to theaters soon—stay tuned! 🎬✨

snippet.title: Simran's Fire Speech on Stage 🔥💯 | "I Do Not Deserve This" 😡 - Simran | JFW Movie Awards 2025
snippet.description:
Simran has completed 30 years of being an actress in the industry and has gained respect and love from all over the world! At the JFW Movie Awards 2025, a grand celebration took place as Simran was honoured by more than 10 actresses such as Keerthy Suresh, Krithi Shetty, Parvathy Thiruvothu, Amala Paul, Sri Gouri Priya, Sriya Reddy, Nikhila VImal, Grace Antony, Swasika and Dushara! Simran's speech was bold as she talks about how she received an unnecessary text from a co-star and that she rather do "Aunty" roles than roles that do not mean anything! 

Simran recently did a cameo in the blockbuster hit "Good Bad Ugly" and was praised for her brilliant performance and her iconic dance was used in the movie with Ajith Kumar!

Watch the video now and let us know your feedback in the comments section below!

Title Sponsor - Twin Birds
Powered By - Chandrika Ayurvedic Soap
Co-presented by - Finesse Fine Mattresses

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: तेरे जैसे राक्षस का खून पीकर ही मैं शांत होऊंगी - विनाशकारी अंत - Prem Granth Last Climax Scene
snippet.description:
Prem Granth is a 1996 Hindi romantic bollywood drama film starring Rishi Kapoor, Madhuri Dixit, Anupam Kher and Om Puri. The story revolves around Somen, son a Hindu priest of the village. Somen falls in love with Kajri who belongs to a lower caste and Somen’s family disapprove their relationship. When Kajri goes missing, Somen leaves his village to stay with his uncle. Will the lovers ever reunite?

💎 Movie : Prem Granth - प्रेम ग्रन्थ (1996)
💎 Director: Rajiv Kapoor - राजीव कपूर 
💎 Cast: 
    Shammi Kapoor - शम्मी कपूर as Nandlal
    Rishi Kapoor - ऋषि कपूर as Somen
    Madhuri Dixit - माधुरी दीक्षित as Kajri
    Anupam Kher - अनुपम खेर as Swami Dharam Bhooshan
    Om Puri - ओम पूरी as Baliram
    Prem Chopra - प्रेम चोपड़ा as Kedar Nath
    Reema Lagoo - रीमा लागू as Parvati
    Himani Shivpuri as Natho
    Sulabha Arya as Laxmi
    Govind Namdeo as Roop Sahai
💎 Music : Laxmikant–Pyarelal - लक्ष्मीकांत - प्यारेलाल

This heartfelt romantic duet is sung by the legendary Udit Narayan and Alka Yagnik, with music composed by Anand-Milind and lyrics by Sameer.

snippet.title: Arranged Marriage Season2 Episode 3 | Good Bad Ugly | RamWedsJanani | Vishnu & Rajithha | ZeroFilter
snippet.description:
#ArrangedMarriage #VishnuUnnikrishnan #ZeroFilter 

Arranged Marriage | Season 2 | Episode 3 | Ram Weds Janani | Vishnu Unnikrishnan | Rajiththa | Divya

Welcome to Arranged Marriage, a heartfelt YouTube series that explores love found in the most unexpected way—through an arranged marriage! Follow the journey of two individuals brought together by family, tradition, and culture, who slowly discover friendship, trust, and eventually, love. Watch how their worlds collide and connect as they navigate new experiences, overcome misunderstandings, and learn what it means to truly love and respect each other.

In Episode 3, witness the couple's bond grow stronger even as new challenges threaten their love! 😍 As their chemistry deepens, an unexpected twist unfolds — the cunning maama, along with a mysterious friend, plots against them. 🕵️‍♂️💔 And just when they think they can trust someone, a close friend turns foe!

Get ready for a rollercoaster of emotions, drama, love, betrayal, and thrilling moments in this must-watch episode! ❤️🔥

✨ Highlights of this episode:

Cute romantic moments

Unexpected betrayal

Maama's evil plans revealed

Stronger love and bonding

👉 Don’t miss this emotional rollercoaster filled with love, care, and real-life relationship drama!

Each episode of Arranged Marriage delves into the beauty of growing affection and genuine connection, showcasing how relationships can blossom in surprising ways. If you enjoy stories of romance, personal growth, and cultural dynamics, subscribe and hit the notification bell for every chapter of this emotional and heartwarming tamil series.

#ArrangedMarriage #VishnuUnnikrishnan #ZeroFilter 

Arranged Marriage | Season 2 | Episode 3 | Ram Weds Janani | Vishnu Unnikrishnan | Rajiththa | Divya

Welcome to Arranged Marriage, a heartfelt YouTube series that explores love found in the most unexpected way—through an arranged marriage! Follow the journey of two individuals brought together by family, tradition, and culture, who slowly discover friendship, trust, and eventually, love. Watch how their worlds collide and connect as they navigate new experiences, overcome misunderstandings, and learn what it means to truly love and respect each other.

In Episode 3, witness the couple's bond grow stronger even as new challenges threaten their love! 😍 As their chemistry deepens, an unexpected twist unfolds — the cunning maama, along with a mysterious friend, plots against them. 🕵️‍♂️💔 And just when they think they can trust someone, a close friend turns foe!

Get ready for a rollercoaster of emotions, drama, love, betrayal, and thrilling moments in this must-watch episode! ❤️🔥

✨ Highlights of this episode:

Cute romantic moments

Unexpected betrayal

Maama's evil plans revealed

Stronger love and bonding

👉 Don’t miss this emotional rollercoaster filled with love, care, and real-life relationship drama!

Each episode of Arranged Marriage delves into the beauty of growing affection and genuine connection, showcasing how relationships can blossom in surprising ways. If you enjoy stories of romance, personal growth, and cultural dynamics, subscribe and hit the notification bell for every chapter of this emotional and heartwarming tamil series.

హో హో హో ఓ ఓ హో

చూపుల్తో గుచ్చి గుచ్చి చంపకే, మేరే హాయ్

ఒలల్ల, 
గుండెల్ని గుల్ల చేసి జారకే, మేరే హాయ్

నీ ప్రేమ కోసం నేను పిచ్చోన్నైపోయానే
నీ ప్రేమ కోసం నేను పిచ్చోన్నైపోయానే
నీ కళ్ళు పేలిపోను చూడవే మేరే హాయ్

మైకమే హాయ్ మైకమే

మైకమే హాయ్ మైకమే
ఏదోలా కొత్తగ ఉంది లోకమే హాయ్ లోకమే
నిలువెల్లా నీరైపోయే దేహమే హాయ్ దేహమే
లైఫంతా అయిపోయింది భారమే, హాయ్
నీ అందం అడవైపోను చూడవే మేరే హాయ్

ఒలల్లా, 
చూపుల్తో గుచ్చి గుచ్చి
చంపకే మేరే హాయ్, హాయ్.

నవ్వుల్తో పిండేస్తావు హృదయమే హాయ్ హృదయమే

నవ్వుల్తో పిండేస్తావు హృదయమే హాయ్ హృదయమే
నిన్ను విడిచి ఉండలేను నిమిషమే హాయ్ నిమిషమే

నీ ఈడు బీడైపోను చూడవే మేరే హాయ్

ఒలల్లా, 
చూపుల్తో గుచ్చి గుచ్చి చంపకే మేరే హాయ్

గుండెల్ని గుల్ల చేసి జారకే, మేరే హాయ్

ఒలల్ల, 
నీ ప్రేమ కోసం నేను పిచ్చోన్నైపోయానే
నీ ప్రేమ కోసం నేను పిచ్చోన్నైపోయానే
నీ కళ్ళు పేలిపోను చూడవే మేరే హాయ్

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Koi Naa | Bhool Chuk Maaf | Rajkummar Rao, Wamiqa Gabbi | Tanishk, Irshad, Shreya, Harnoor, Gifty
snippet.description:
Sang tere rehna khayal banke,
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na!
 
Presenting the first song release ‘Koi Naa’ from ‘Bhool Chuk Maaf’, featuring Rajkummar Rao and Wamiqa Gabbi! Composed by Tanishk Bagchi and Gifty, it is sung by Harnoor and Shreya Ghoshal and penned by Irshad Kamil. Perfect to dedicate to someone who’s a romantic, let this speak the words of your heart to that special someone!
 
#KoiNaa #ShreyaGhoshal #Harnoor #TanishkBagchi #Gifty #irshadKamil #RajkummarRao #WamiqaGabbi #BhoolChukMaaf
 
Song credits:
Title : Koi Naa
Singers : Harnoor & Shreya Ghoshal
Composers : Tanishk Bagchi & Gifty
Music Production : Tanishk Bagchi & Ganesh Waghela
Lyricist : Irshad Kamil
Language : Hindi
Mix Master : Eric Pillai @ Future sound of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer : Michael Edwin Pillai
Original Punjabi Music & Lyrics : Gifty
Original Song Licensed by Jatt Life Studios
 
Maddock Films presents #BhoolChukMaaf
In cinemas on 9th May
Cast: Rajkummar Rao, Wamiqa Gabbi, Sanjay Mishra, Seema Pahwa, Zakir Hussain, Raghubir Yadav, Ishtiyak Khan, Anubha Fatehpuria
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan
Directed By: Karan Sharma
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota
Music By: Tanishk Bagchi
Background Score: Ketan Sodha
Story Screenplay & Dialogues By: Karan Sharma
Director Of Photography: Sudeep Chatterjee
Lyrics: Irshad Kamil
Director of Choreography: Vijay A Ganguly
 
Lyrics:

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na
 
Kehta hai tujhko haseen aaina
Tujh mein hi rehta hai leen aaina
Bolo isey mujhko jalaya na kare
Lena maine tujhse ye chheen aaina
 
Mujhse hi sun le tareef apni
Shaadi wali milti lakeer apni
Teri meri duniya basegi jis mein
Aane wali jaldi tareekh apni

Tu to mere surmey jaisa
Tu to mere sapne jaisa
Akhiyon Mein
Rakhna hai
Sabse chhupa ke tujhko
Chupke se
Marzi se
Chaahungi  tujhko

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Dilon ki ameeri mein gareeb koi na
Ashiqon se badh ke ajeeb koi na
Aankhein milein jab tab Jaan pe baney
Ishqey se oonchi to saleeb koi na
 
(Tere jaisa ik mera Yaar aaina
Chadhti jawani ka shingaar aaina
Dekho mujhe kitna guroor ho gaya
Leke aayin mujhpe nikhaar aaina)

Chura le mujhe ab Sajjana tu saara
Jawani tere naam kar di maine yaara
Laga ke tujhe honth se apne dekhun
Kahan se tu m meetha kahan se khaara

Paaniyon pe behte chiraag jaisi tu
Mehke gulaabon ke hai baag jaisi tu
Thandi hoti akkhiyann tujhe dekh ke
Chhooney se to lagti hai aag jaisi tu
 
Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Tera mera ek jaisa haal ho gaya
Dooriyon mein rahna mohaal ho gaya
Le ke aaja jaldi. Baraat maahiya
Rang meri menhdi ka laal ho gaya
 
Tu to mere surmey jaisa
Tu to mere sapne jaisa
Akhiyon Mein
Rakhna hai
Sabse chhupa ke tujhko
Chupke se
Marzi se
Chaahungi  tujhko

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Main tere pe mar gayi sajna re
Tu samjha na
Ishq se main bhar gayi sajna re
Tu samjha na
Tere aage peechhe ghoomti phirun
Piye bina hi main jhoomti phirun
Tere saaye ko bhi choomti phirun
Meri jaan
Tujhpe nisaar sajna

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

hawa mein huddi woh ka tale kho gayi, han kho gayi

o dekho dekho sab ghum raha hai, dekho dekho jag jhoom raha hai

snippet.title: Superman | Superman Day - Behind The Scenes Look
snippet.description:
We’re just getting started. #Superman - Only in Theaters and @imax, July 11 #LookUp #SupermanDay 

“Superman,” DC Studios’ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures. In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who’s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (“Twisters,” “Hollywood”) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (“The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel”) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the “X-Men” movies, “Juror #2”) as Lex Luthor. The film also stars Edi Gathegi (“For All Mankind”), Anthony Carrigan (“Barry,” “Gotham”), Nathan Fillion (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “The Suicide Squad”), Isabela Merced (“Alien Romulus”), Skyler Gisondo (“Licorice Pizza,” “Booksmart”), Sara Sampaio (“At Midnight”), María Gabriela de Faría (“The Moodys”),
Wendell Pierce (“Selma,” “Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan”), Alan Tudyk (“Andor”), Pruitt Taylor Vince (“Bird Box”) and Neva Howell (“Greedy People”).

“Superman” is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther. Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (“The Last of Us”), editors William Hoy (“The Batman”), Jason Ballantine (the “IT” films, “The Flash”) and Craig Alpert (“Deadpool 2,” “Blue Beetle”).

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, “Superman,” which will be in theaters and IMAX® nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

હે એને ભુલી નતો શકતો મોડ મોડ રે ભુલો...(૨)
બસસ્ટેન્ડ આઈ બસ ઉભી રહી દરવાજો ખુલો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો
હે જોઇ ઝાટકો વાગ્યો દિલ ને વગર પીધે હુ ડોલ્યો
કાળજા કપાણા મારા બળ્યો પણ હુ ના બોલ્યો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો
હે એના હામુ હુ જોઈરો મારા પ્યાર હુ ખોઇરો...(૨)
હે જુની યાદો તાજી થઈ જઈ જોઈ જીવ બળ્યો 
મારુ હૈયુ રે ભરાઈ ગયુ હિબકે હિબકે હુ રોયો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો...(૨)

હે જોઈ હૈયુ રે હિબકાઈ ગયુ મારા દલડા રે દુભાણા
એ મને દુઃખી જોઈ પોપણ એના પણ ભીજાણા
હો હો હેડવુ મારે થઈ ગયુ ત્યાથી પગ મારો ના ઉપડે
ઘડી ઘડી નજર મારી એના હોમી ઉપડે
હે મારો પ્યાર મારો રહ્યો નથી પુરી બીજા મન મડી પોખી...(૨)
હે રોમ રોમ માં લાય લાગી અંદર અંદર હુ બળ્યો 
દુઃખ થયુ દિલ માં ઘણું પણ કઈ બોલી ના શકયો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો...(૨)

હે તમે સાસરે જાશો તમારા અમે દુઃખ માં દાઝતા રેશુ
રોઇ રોઇ રાતો ઘાઢશુ પણ કોઇ ના કેશુ
હે તારા નામ ની હૈયા બળતરા મને કોટા ની જેમ વાગે
તુ પારકા ની પરણેતર તારા પર હક ના મારો લાગે
હે લખાયુ હસે થવાનુ રે જુદા યાદ આવશે તારી સદા...(૨)
હે એની આશા છોડી દિધી રોઈ રદો રે વાળ્યો
દુઃખી રઈશુ આખી જીંદગી નહિ મળે સુખ નો છાયો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો...(3)

બસસ્ટેન્ડ આઈ બસ ઉભી રહી દરવાજો ખુલો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો
હે જોઇ ઝાટકો વાગ્યો દિલ ને વગર પીધે હુ ડોલ્યો
કાળજા કપાણા મારા બળ્યો પણ હુ ના બોલ્યો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો
હે એના હામુ હુ જોઈરો મારા પ્યાર હુ ખોઇરો...(૨)
હે જુની યાદો તાજી થઈ જઈ જોઈ જીવ બળ્યો 
મારુ હૈયુ રે ભરાઈ ગયુ હિબકે હિબકે હુ રોયો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો...(૨)

હે જોઈ હૈયુ રે હિબકાઈ ગયુ મારા દલડા રે દુભાણા
એ મને દુઃખી જોઈ પોપણ એના પણ ભીજાણા
હો હો હેડવુ મારે થઈ ગયુ ત્યાથી પગ મારો ના ઉપડે
ઘડી ઘડી નજર મારી એના હોમી ઉપડે
હે મારો પ્યાર મારો રહ્યો નથી પુરી બીજા મન મડી પોખી...(૨)
હે રોમ રોમ માં લાય લાગી અંદર અંદર હુ બળ્યો 
દુઃખ થયુ દિલ માં ઘણું પણ કઈ બોલી ના શકયો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો...(૨)

હે તમે સાસરે જાશો તમારા અમે દુઃખ માં દાઝતા રેશુ
રોઇ રોઇ રાતો ઘાઢશુ પણ કોઇ ના કેશુ
હે તારા નામ ની હૈયા બળતરા મને કોટા ની જેમ વાગે
તુ પારકા ની પરણેતર તારા પર હક ના મારો લાગે
હે લખાયુ હસે થવાનુ રે જુદા યાદ આવશે તારી સદા...(૨)
હે એની આશા છોડી દિધી રોઈ રદો રે વાળ્યો
દુઃખી રઈશુ આખી જીંદગી નહિ મળે સુખ નો છાયો
હે સાસરે થી આયા પિયાર માં હારે પતિ ને જોયો...(3)

snippet.description:
Danny Boyle and Alex Garland reunite for #28YearsLater – exclusively in movie theatres 6.20. 

Follow Us on Social:

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

Academy Award®-winning director Danny Boyle and Academy Award®-nominated writer Alex Garland reunite for 28 Years Later, a terrifying new story set in the world created by 28 Days Later. It’s been almost three decades since the rage virus escaped a biological weapons laboratory, and now, still in a ruthlessly enforced quarantine, some have found ways to exist amidst the infected. One such group of survivors lives on a small island connected to the mainland by a single, heavily-defended causeway. When one of the group leaves the island on a mission into the dark heart of the mainland, he discovers secrets, wonders, and horrors that have mutated not only the infected but other survivors as well.
 
Directed by:​​
Danny Boyle​​​
​
Written by:​​​​
Alex Garland​​​

Alex Garland

snippet.title: क्यों हमे जीते जी मार डालना चाहती हैं Prem Granth Movie Scene - Madhuri - Sulbha Arya - Om Puri
snippet.description:
Prem Granth is a 1996 Hindi romantic bollywood drama film starring Rishi Kapoor, Madhuri Dixit, Anupam Kher and Om Puri. The story revolves around Somen, son a Hindu priest of the village. Somen falls in love with Kajri who belongs to a lower caste and Somen’s family disapprove their relationship. When Kajri goes missing, Somen leaves his village to stay with his uncle. Will the lovers ever reunite?

💎 Movie : Prem Granth - प्रेम ग्रन्थ (1996)
💎 Director: Rajiv Kapoor - राजीव कपूर 
💎 Cast: 
    Shammi Kapoor - शम्मी कपूर as Nandlal
    Rishi Kapoor - ऋषि कपूर as Somen
    Madhuri Dixit - माधुरी दीक्षित as Kajri
    Anupam Kher - अनुपम खेर as Swami Dharam Bhooshan
    Om Puri - ओम पूरी as Baliram
    Prem Chopra - प्रेम चोपड़ा as Kedar Nath
    Reema Lagoo - रीमा लागू as Parvati
    Himani Shivpuri as Natho
    Sulabha Arya as Laxmi
    Govind Namdeo as Roop Sahai
💎 Music : Laxmikant–Pyarelal - लक्ष्मीकांत - प्यारेलाल

पोर कट्यार...

छबिदार गुलजार..
लई ग्वाड ही ऊसावानी रं..
घोर जीवा आहे रं..

लई देखनी, हरनीवानी..
पोरं ही अंगार..
घोर लाविती, याड लाविती..
पिरमाचा काहूर..

ठावं नाही जी काही..
सैरंभैरं म्या झालो..

तुझ्या नादातं..

व्हटावं आली रं..
पोराचा बाजार उठला रं..

रानी तुझ्या मागं..

भूक नाही, तानभी गं..
पूनवाचा तू चांद..

नजरनं ठार कर तू..
नजरनं लाज तू..
चांदनं टिपूर तू..
नजरनं ठार कर तू..

ठावं नाही जी काही..
सैरंभैरं म्या झालो..
जीव वतून गेलं.. 
तुझ्या नादातं..

दिलाची धडधड..
व्हटावं आली रं..
पोराचा बाजार उठला रं..
